column1: File Name: JornadaStudy_086_smes_plant_cover_line_data.csv    Last Update: 03/27/2012    By: John P. Anderson
File header updated by Ken Ramsey on 01/23/2013.
Dataset: SMES vegetation line intercept data [Dataset ID: DSL2006014]
Project: Small Mammal Exclosure Study [Project ID: PRL2006022]
date    - Date data was collected [mm/dd/yyyy]
site    - Site location code [C=Creosotebush, G=Grassland]
block   - Block Number [1-4]
plot    - Plot number [1-4]
treatment - Treatment type [C=Control, R=Rodent Exclosuer, L=Laghmorph
Exclosure, B=Bovine Exclosure
line    - Line number [Begins at quad 1,3,and 5]
spp - Species Code, see SMESSPP.LST for complete species code
listing.
intercept   - Distance from beginning of line (0 cm) to beginning of
perennial species intercept along tape (cm)
id      - Analog cassette tape label
comment_code - Comment code (0=No comment / 1=See data history log)
keyfield - spatial primary key field (specific to Jornada Information Management System [JIMS])
datasetid - old dataset identifier (specific to JIMS)
POINT_X - x spatial coodinate [NEED COORDINATE SYSTEM, DATUM, PROJECTION SYSTEM, ...] (specific to JIMS)
POINT_Y -  y spatial coodinate [NEED COORDINATE SYSTEM, DATUM, PROJECTION SYSTEM, ...] (specific to JIMS)
table_id - data table id (specific to JIMS)
layer_id - spatial layer id (specific to JIMS)
date
